---
title: Cajun Shrimp Chopped Salad with Charred Corn, Tomatoes & Creamy Caesar Dressing
description: Looking for a flavorful, feel-good salad with a pop of protein? This chopped salad perfectly balances smoky and sweet flavors, thanks to Cajun-spiced shrimp and charred corn, tossed with juicy grape tomatoes and fresh lettuce. Everything’s tossed in a tangy, lemony Caesar dressing for a creamy finish that brings the whole bowl together. So, what are you waiting for? Add this meal to your box! Chop-chop!
